title: SR-71 Documentary
description:
1990 documentary during a pivotal time in military and agency history as things went from aircraft to space-based surveillance.  Now we see a return to airspace compliments of the growing use of drones.  God help us all this is the ingredients of Skynet.

- Big Papi
